Dear participant,
<p>Thank you for participating in the SMILE research study.</p>
<p>When you completed the survey, you stated that you may be willing to recruit other people to take the survey.</p>
<p>
  You can recruit up to 2 additional people. For each person you recruit who
  successfully completes the survey, you will receive a small payment of $2 [specific to country], 
  and the person completing the survey will receive a small payment as well.
</p>
<p>If you would like to recruit other people to join the research study, please click on the link below to learn more.</p>
